title: BONUS: Danny & Chrishell Stause (Selling Sunset) & Ronen Rubinstein (9-1-1 Lonestar)
itunes:title: BONUS: Danny & Chrishell Stause (Selling Sunset) & Ronen Rubinstein (9-1-1 Lonestar)
description:
In a special bonus episode, Danny chats with author and star of Selling Sunset on Netflix, Chrishell Stause, about her new book Under Construction (out FEB 8), her dating life, and Selling Sunset. After their talk, Danny sits down with Ronen Rubinstein, who plays TK Strand on 9-1-1 Lonestar on FOX about bisexual representation in media, working with Ryan Murphy, Tarlos, new music, and more!


Ronen Interview: 30:00ish
